<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>A More Beauty</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <script charset="utf-8" src="https://static.line-scdn.net/liff/edge/2/sdk.js"></script>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <script src="https://unpkg.com/vue@3/dist/vue.global.js"></script>
  <script src="https://www.gstatic.com/firebasejs/8.10.1/firebase-app.js"></script>
  <script src="https://www.gstatic.com/firebasejs/8.10.1/firebase-firestore.js"></script>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons+Outlined" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@300;400;500;700&family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif; background-color: #F9F7F5; color: #4A4A4A; }
    .font-serif { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; }
    .btn-gold { background-color: #C4A484; color: white; transition: all 0.3s; }
    .admin-card { background: white; border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
    .calendar-day-active { background-color: #C4A484; color: white; border-radius: 50%; }
    .calendar-day-disabled { color: #E5E7EB; cursor: not-allowed; pointer-events: none; }
    .admin-day-selected { border: 2px solid #C4A484; border-radius: 50%; font-weight: bold; }
    .invitation-card { background: #FFFFFF; border: 1px solid #E5E5E5; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); position: relative; }
    .invitation-card::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 10px; left: 10px; right: 10px; bottom: 10px; border: 1px solid #C4A484; pointer-events: none; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div id="app" class="min-h-screen relative">
  <div v-if="configError" class="fixed inset-0 bg-black/90 z-[999] flex items-center justify-center p-8 text-white text-center whitespace-pre-wrap font-mono">{{ configError }}</div>

  <div v-if="loading" class="fixed inset-0 bg-white/90 z-50 flex items-center justify-center flex-col">
    <div class="animate-spin rounded-full h-12 w-12 border-t-2 border-b-2 border-[#C4A484] mb-3"></div>
    <p class="text-xs text-stone-400">{{ loadingText }}</p>
  </div>

  <div v-if="view === 'login'" class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-screen p-8 bg-[#FAF8F6]">
    <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-[#E5Ddd5] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6"><span class="material-icons-outlined text-4xl text-white">lock</span></div>
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#5D4E46] mb-10 tracking-wider">店務管理系統</h1>
    <input v-model="adminPassword" type="password" class="w-full max-w-sm p-4 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm text-center tracking-[0.5em] mb-4 outline-none" placeholder="••••••">
    <button @click="loginAdmin" class="w-full max-w-sm py-4 bg-[#C4A484] text-white rounded-xl font-bold shadow-lg mb-4">登入</button>
    <button @click="view = 'home'" class="text-gray-400 text-sm">返回前台</button>
  </div>

  <div v-if="view === 'admin'" class="pb-24 bg-[#F9F7F5] min-h-screen">
    <div class="bg-white p-6 sticky top-0 z-20 shadow-sm flex justify-between items-center">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#5D4E46]">管理後台</h2>
      <button @click="view = 'home'" class="material-icons-outlined text-gray-500">logout</button>
    </div>
    <div class="flex gap-3 p-4">
      <button @click="adminTab='schedule'" :class="['px-4 py-2 rounded-xl text-sm font-bold', adminTab==='schedule'?'bg-[#C4A484] text-white':'bg-white text-gray-400']">排班</button>
      <button @click="adminTab='bookings';fetchBookings()" :class="['px-4 py-2 rounded-xl text-sm font-bold', adminTab==='bookings'?'bg-[#C4A484] text-white':'bg-white text-gray-400']">訂單</button>
    </div>

    <div v-if="adminTab === 'schedule'" class="p-4 space-y-4">
      <div class="flex gap-2 mb-4">
         <button @click="adminStudio='Yilan';fetchAdminSchedule()" :class="['flex-1 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold border', adminStudio==='Yilan'?'border-[#C4A484] text-[#C4A484] bg-white':'border-transparent text-gray-400']">宜蘭館</button>
         <button @click="adminStudio='Taipei';fetchAdminSchedule()" :class="['flex-1 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold border', adminStudio==='Taipei'?'border-[#C4A484] text-[#C4A484] bg-white':'border-transparent text-gray-400']">台北館</button>
      </div>
      <div class="admin-card p-6">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-4">
          <span class="font-bold text-[#5D4E46]">{{ currentYear }} / {{ currentMonth + 1 }}</span>
          <div><button @click="changeMonth(-1)" class="px-2">◀</button><button @click="changeMonth(1)" class="px-2">▶</button></div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-7 gap-y-4 text-center">
           <div v-for="d in ['日','一','二','三','四','五','六']" class="text-gray-300 text-xs">{{ d }}</div>
           <div v-for="n in firstDayOfWeek" :key="'e'+n"></div>
           <button v-for="day in daysInMonth" :key="day" @click="adminSelectDate(day)"
                   class="h-8 w-8 mx-auto rounded-full relative flex items-center justify-center"
                   :class="adminSelectedDate === formatDate(day) ? 'admin-day-selected' : ''">
             <span :class="adminOpenDates.includes(formatDate(day)) ? 'text-[#5D4E46] font-bold' : 'text-gray-300'">{{ day }}</span>
             <div v-if="adminOpenDates.includes(formatDate(day))" class="absolute -bottom-1 w-1 h-1 bg-green-400 rounded-full"></div>
           </button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div v-if="adminSelectedDate" class="fixed bottom-0 left-0 right-0 bg-white p-6 border-t z-30 flex gap-4">
         <button @click="toggleOpenDate(false)" :class="['flex-1 py-3 rounded-xl font-bold', !adminOpenDates.includes(adminSelectedDate)?'bg-gray-800 text-white':'bg-gray-100']">店休</button>
         <button @click="toggleOpenDate(true)" :class="['flex-1 py-3 rounded-xl font-bold', adminOpenDates.includes(adminSelectedDate)?'bg-green-500 text-white':'bg-green-100 text-green-600']">營業</button>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div v-if="adminTab === 'bookings'" class="p-4 space-y-4">
       <div v-for="order in bookings" :key="order.id" class="admin-card p-4 border-l-4 border-[#C4A484]">
          <div class="flex justify-between font-bold text-[#5D4E46]"><span>{{ order.name }}</span><span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-gray-100">{{ order.studio_name }}</span></div>
          <div class="text-sm mt-1">{{ order.date }} {{ order.time }}</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-1">{{ order.services }}</div>
       </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div v-if="view === 'home'" class="flex-grow flex flex-col max-w-lg mx-auto w-full bg-white shadow-xl min-h-screen relative">
    <header class="p-6 text-center sticky top-0 bg-white/95 backdrop-blur z-20 border-b border-stone-100 relative">
      <div class="w-32 h-32 mx-auto mb-2 rounded-full overflow-hidden border-2 border-[#C4A484] p-1"><img :src="logoSrc" class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-full"></div>
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-serif text-[#C4A484] tracking-widest font-bold">A More Beauty</h1>
      <div @click="secretClick" class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-16 h-16 z-50"></div> 
    </header>

    <main class="flex-grow p-6 flex flex-col pb-24"> 
      <div v-if="step === 0">
        <div class="text-center mb-8"><h2 class="text-xl text-stone-700 font-light">喚醒肌膚原本的光彩<br>預見更好的自己</h2><div class="h-0.5 w-12 bg-[#C4A484] mx-auto mt-4"></div><p v-if="userProfile.name" class="mt-4 text-[#C4A484] text-sm">Welcome, {{ userProfile.name }}</p></div>
        <div v-if="!quizCompleted" class="bg-[#FAF8F6] p-6 rounded-lg mb-8 border border-stone-100">
           <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4 text-[#C4A484]"><span class="material-icons-outlined">psychology</span><span class="font-bold">30秒肌膚對話</span></div>
           <div v-if="quizStep < quizQuestions.length">
             <h3 class="text-lg font-medium mb-4 text-stone-700">{{ quizQuestions[quizStep].q }}</h3>
             <div class="grid gap-3"><button v-for="opt in quizQuestions[quizStep].options" @click="answerQuiz(opt)" class="text-left p-3 bg-white border border-stone-200 rounded hover:border-[#C4A484]">{{ opt }}</button></div>
           </div>
        </div>
        <div v-if="quizCompleted" class="bg-[#FAF8F6] p-6 rounded-lg mb-8 border border-[#C4A484]">
           <h3 class="text-[#C4A484] font-bold mb-2">建議療程：</h3><p class="text-stone-600 font-medium text-lg">{{ recommendedService }}</p>
           <button @click="resetQuiz" class="flex items-center text-xs text-stone-400 mt-4"><span class="material-icons-outlined text-sm mr-1">refresh</span>重新測驗</button>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-4">
            <button @click="selectStudio('Yilan')" class="p-6 border rounded-xl hover:border-[#C4A484] text-center"><div class="font-bold text-stone-700">宜蘭館</div></button>
            <button @click="selectStudio('Taipei')" class="p-6 border rounded-xl hover:border-[#C4A484] text-center"><div class="font-bold text-stone-700">台北館</div></button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div v-if="step === 1">
         <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-6"><button @click="changeMonth(-1)">◀</button><span class="text-lg font-medium">{{ currentYear }} / {{ currentMonth + 1 }}</span><button @click="changeMonth(1)">▶</button></div>
         <div class="grid grid-cols-7 gap-y-4 text-center mb-6">
           <div v-for="d in ['日','一','二','三','四','五','六']" class="text-stone-400 text-xs">{{ d }}</div>
           <div v-for="n in firstDayOfWeek" :key="'e'+n"></div>
           <button v-for="day in daysInMonth" :key="day" :disabled="!isDateOpen(day)" @click="selectDate(day)" :class="['h-8 w-8 mx-auto rounded-full', selectedDate === formatDate(day) ? 'bg-[#C4A484] text-white' : '', !isDateOpen(day) ? 'text-gray-200 pointer-events-none' : 'text-stone-700']">{{ day }}</button>
         </div>
         <div v-if="selectedDate">
            <h3 class="text-sm text-stone-500 mb-3 text-center">時段</h3>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-3 mb-6"><button v-for="time in timeSlots" :key="time" @click="selectTime(time)" :class="['py-2 border rounded-lg text-sm', selectedTime === time ? 'bg-[#C4A484] text-white border-[#C4A484]' : 'border-stone-200']">{{ time }}</button></div>
         </div>
         <div class="text-center text-xs text-gray-400 mt-8">灰字為未開放預約，請洽官方 LINE</div>
      </div>

      <div v-if="step === 2">
         <h2 class="text-xl text-center mb-2 font-serif">選擇療程</h2>
         <p class="text-center text-xs text-stone-500 mb-6">{{ selectedDate }} {{ selectedTime }}<br>(若選兩項，自動檢查下個時段)</p>
         <div v-if="errorMsg" class="bg-red-50 text-red-500 text-sm p-3 rounded mb-4 text-center">{{ errorMsg }}</div>
         <div class="space-y-3 mb-20">
            <div v-for="(srv, index) in services" :key="index" @click="toggleService(srv.name)" :class="['flex items-center p-4 border rounded-xl', selectedServices.includes(srv.name) ? 'border-[#C4A484] bg-[#FAF8F6]' : 'border-stone-200']">
               <div class="flex-grow"><div class="font-medium text-stone-800">{{ srv.name }}</div><div class="text-xs text-stone-400">{{ srv.desc }}</div></div>
               <span class="material-icons-outlined text-[#C4A484]" v-if="selectedServices.includes(srv.name)">check_box</span>
               <span class="material-icons-outlined text-stone-200" v-else>check_box_outline_blank</span>
            </div>
         </div>
      </div>

      <div v-if="step === 3">
         <h2 class="text-xl text-center mb-6 font-serif">資料確認</h2>
         <div class="space-y-5">
            <input v-model="form.name" class="w-full p-3 border rounded-lg bg-gray-50" readonly>
            <input v-model="form.phone" type="tel" class="w-full p-3 border rounded-lg" placeholder="電話" required>
            <textarea v-model="form.notes" class="w-full p-3 border rounded-lg" placeholder="備註"></textarea>
         </div>
         <button @click="goToConfirmation" class="w-full btn-gold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg text-lg font-bold mt-8 shadow-lg">下一步</button>
      </div>

      <div v-if="step === 4" class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center h-full">
         <div class="invitation-card w-full p-8 text-center max-w-sm mx-auto bg-white">
            <div class="text-xs text-stone-400 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4">INVITATION</div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-[#C4A484] mb-6">A More Beauty</h2>
            <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
               <div class="text-lg font-medium text-stone-800">{{ selectedServices.join(' + ') }}</div>
               <div class="h-px bg-stone-100 w-1/2 mx-auto"></div>
               <div class="text-lg font-medium text-stone-800">{{ selectedDate }}<br>{{ selectedTime }}</div>
               <div class="text-sm text-stone-500">{{ studio==='Taipei'?'台北館':'宜蘭館' }}</div>
            </div>
            <button @click="submitBooking" class="w-full btn-gold py-3 px-6 rounded text-sm font-bold shadow-lg">確認預約</button>
         </div>
      </div>

      <div v-if="step === 5" class="text-center pt-10 px-6">
         <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-[#C4A484] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 text-white animate-bounce"><span class="material-icons-outlined text-4xl">check</span></div>
         <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-stone-800 mb-4">預約成功</h2>
         <p class="text-stone-600 mb-6">預約卡已發送至您的 LINE。</p>
         <a :href="LINE_URL" target="_top" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-full btn-gold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg font-bold shadow-lg mb-4">返回官方 LINE</a>
      </div>
    </main>

    <footer v-if="step > 0 && step < 5" class="fixed bottom-0 left-0 right-0 p-4 bg-white border-t border-stone-100 flex justify-between z-30 max-w-lg mx-auto">
       <button @click="prevStep" class="flex items-center text-stone-400">上一步</button>
       <button v-if="canProceed" @click="step++" class="btn-gold px-6 py-2 rounded shadow-md">下一步</button>
    </footer>
  </div>
</div>

<script>
// ===========================================
// ⚠️ 只要修改這裡 (請填入剛剛那三把鑰匙)
// ===========================================

// 1. Firebase 設定 (複製整段貼上)
const firebaseConfig = {
  apiKey: "AIzaSyCNF3n8XhuqjUOrZHBHUrDC6SgH-M9lZlA",
  authDomain: "amore-beauty-booking.firebaseapp.com",
  projectId: "amore-beauty-booking",
  storageBucket: "amore-beauty-booking.firebasestorage.app",
  messagingSenderId: "128469996282",
  appId: "1:128469996282:web:b45fc34167f6f9fa63ef43"
};

// 2. 您的其他設定
const LIFF_ID = "2008670533-YB72k6Wm"; 
const MAKE_WEBHOOK_URL = "
https://hook.eu1.make.com/xau76y1e63gjulan76p1uomn2drsxxai"; 
const LINE_URL = "https://lin.ee/tBiHfOD"; // 加好友連結
const LOGO_SRC = "data:image/png;base64,"; 

// ===========================================

const { createApp, ref, computed, onMounted } = Vue;
createApp({
  setup() {
    // 檢查設定是否正確
    const configError = ref('');
    if(firebaseConfig.apiKey.includes("請貼上") || LIFF_ID.includes("請貼上")) {
        configError.value = "⚠️ 設定尚未完成！\n請用記事本打開 index.html\n填入 Firebase 設定 與 LIFF ID。";
    }

    if (!firebase.apps.length) firebase.initializeApp(firebaseConfig);
    const db = firebase.firestore();

    const view = ref('home'); const step = ref(0); const loading = ref(false); const loadingText = ref('連線中...');
    const secretCount = ref(0); const adminPassword = ref(''); const userProfile = ref({ userId: '', name: '' });
    const adminTab = ref('schedule'); const adminStudio = ref('Yilan'); const adminSelectedDate = ref(''); const adminOpenDates = ref([]); const bookings = ref([]);
    const studio = ref(''); const currentYear = ref(new Date().getFullYear()); const currentMonth = ref(new Date().getMonth());
    const selectedDate = ref(''); const selectedTime = ref(''); const selectedServices = ref([]); const form = ref({ name: '', phone: '', notes: '' }); const errorMsg = ref('');
    const timeSlots = ['11:00', '13:00', '15:00', '17:00', '19:00'];
    const services = [
      { name: 'AGEs抗醣膠原調理', desc: '回復肌膚彈性' }, { name: '晶鑽生肌煥膚', desc: '亮白光澤護理' },
      { name: '緊緻微波拉提', desc: '非侵入式拉提' }, { name: '完美無瑕液態薇秒', desc: '細緻膚質' },
      { name: '精油舒壓 SPA 60 mins', desc: '全身放鬆' }, { name: '精油舒壓 SPA 90 mins', desc: '深層放鬆' },
      { name: '頭部抗壓 SPA', desc: '釋放腦壓' }, { name: '小香肩美形雕塑', desc: '肩頸線條' },
      { name: '女神美背無暇嫩膚調理', desc: '背部護理' }, { name: '婦科暖宮護理', desc: '溫暖呵護' },
      { name: '彈力美胸護理', desc: '胸部保養' }, { name: '體雕 - 方案 A：纖體熱能脂雕 (RF)', desc: '熱能緊緻' },
      { name: '體雕 - 方案 B：爆脂音塑體雕', desc: '體態雕塑' }, { name: '耳燭SPA', desc: '顱內淨化' }
    ];

    onMounted(async () => {
        try {
            await liff.init({ liffId: LIFF_ID });
            if (!liff.isLoggedIn()) {
                console.log("未登入，進入手動模式"); // 避免白畫面
            } else {
                const p = await liff.getProfile();
                userProfile.value = { userId: p.userId, name: p.displayName };
                form.value.name = p.displayName;
            }
        } catch(e) { console.log("LIFF Error", e); }
    });

    const secretClick = () => { secretCount.value++; if(secretCount.value >= 5) { view.value = 'login'; secretCount.value=0; } };
    const loginAdmin = () => { if(adminPassword.value==='12345'){ view.value='admin'; fetchAdminSchedule(); fetchBookings(); } else alert('密碼錯誤'); };
    
    const fetchAdminSchedule = async () => {
        const docId = `schedule_${adminStudio.value}_${currentYear.value}_${currentMonth.value}`;
        try {
            const doc = await db.collection('settings').doc(docId).get();
            adminOpenDates.value = doc.exists ? (doc.data().openDates || []) : [];
        } catch(e) { console.error(e); }
        adminSelectedDate.value = '';
    };
    const adminSelectDate = (d) => adminSelectedDate.value = formatDate(d);
    const toggleOpenDate = async (isOpen) => {
        if(!adminSelectedDate.value) return;
        let newDates = [...adminOpenDates.value]; const t = adminSelectedDate.value;
        if(isOpen) { if(!newDates.includes(t)) newDates.push(t); } else { newDates = newDates.filter(d=>d!==t); }
        adminOpenDates.value = newDates;
        const docId = `schedule_${adminStudio.value}_${currentYear.value}_${currentMonth.value}`;
        await db.collection('settings').doc(docId).set({ openDates: newDates }, { merge: true });
    };
    const fetchBookings = async () => {
        try {
            const snap = await db.collection('bookings').orderBy('createdAt', 'desc').limit(20).get();
            bookings.value = snap.docs.map(d => ({id:d.id, ...d.data()}));
        } catch(e) { console.error(e); }
    };

    const selectStudio = (s) => { studio.value = s; adminStudio.value = s; fetchAdminSchedule(); step.value = 1; };
    const isDateOpen = (d) => adminOpenDates.value.includes(formatDate(d));
    const toggleService = (name) => {
        errorMsg.value = ''; const isSel = !selectedServices.value.includes(name);
        if(isSel && selectedServices.value.length >= 1) {
            const tIdx = timeSlots.indexOf(selectedTime.value);
            if(tIdx >= timeSlots.length - 1) { errorMsg.value = "時段過晚，無法預約兩項"; return; }
        }
        if(!isSel) selectedServices.value = selectedServices.value.filter(i=>i!==name);
        else { if(selectedServices.value.length < 2) selectedServices.value.push(name); else errorMsg.value = "最多兩項"; }
    };
    
    const submitBooking = async () => {
        loading.value = true; loadingText.value = "製作預約卡中...";
        const data = {
            userId: userProfile.value.userId, name: form.value.name, phone: form.value.phone,
            studio: studio.value, studio_name: studio.value==='Taipei'?'台北館':'宜蘭館',
            date: selectedDate.value, time: selectedTime.value, services: selectedServices.value.join(' + '),
            notes: form.value.notes, createdAt: new Date().toISOString()
        };
        try {
            await db.collection('bookings').add(data);
            if (!MAKE_WEBHOOK_URL.includes("請貼上")) {
                await fetch(MAKE_WEBHOOK_URL, { method: 'POST', headers: {'Content-Type': 'application/json'}, body: JSON.stringify(data)});
            }
            loading.value = false; step.value = 5;
        } catch(e) { alert('送出失敗'); loading.value = false; }
    };

    const daysInMonth = computed(() => new Date(currentYear.value, currentMonth.value + 1, 0).getDate());
    const firstDayOfWeek = computed(() => new Date(currentYear.value, currentMonth.value, 1).getDay());
    const changeMonth = (d) => { let dt = new Date(currentYear.value, currentMonth.value + d, 1); currentYear.value = dt.getFullYear(); currentMonth.value = dt.getMonth(); fetchAdminSchedule(); };
    const formatDate = (d) => `${currentYear.value}-${String(currentMonth.value + 1).padStart(2,'0')}-${String(d).padStart(2,'0')}`;
    const selectDate = (d) => { selectedDate.value = formatDate(d); selectedTime.value = ''; };
    const selectTime = (t) => { selectedTime.value = t; selectedServices.value = []; errorMsg.value = ''; };
    const calculateEndTime = () => { if(!selectedTime.value) return ''; let [h] = selectedTime.value.split(':').map(Number); return `${h + selectedServices.value.length * 2}:00`; };
    const canProceed = computed(() => { if (step.value === 1) return selectedDate.value && selectedTime.value; if (step.value === 2) return selectedServices.value.length > 0; return true; });
    const prevStep = () => { step.value--; if(step.value === 1) selectedServices.value = []; };
    const nextStep = () => step.value++; const goToConfirmation = () => step.value = 4;
    const quizCompleted = ref(false); const quizStep = ref(0); const recommendedService = ref('');
    const quizQuestions = [ { q: "肌膚狀況？", options: ["乾燥", "暗沉", "水腫"] }, { q: "想改善？", options: ["疲憊", "膚色", "肥胖"] }, { q: "效果？", options: ["緊緻", "發亮", "S曲線"] } ];
    const answerQuiz = () => { recommendedService.value = '精油舒壓 SPA'; quizCompleted.value = true; };
    const resetQuiz = () => { quizCompleted.value = false; };

    return { 
        view, step, loading, loadingText, logoSrc: LOGO_SRC, LINE_URL, userProfile, configError,
        adminPassword, adminTab, adminStudio, adminOpenDates, adminSelectedDate, bookings, 
        currentYear, currentMonth, daysInMonth, firstDayOfWeek, changeMonth, formatDate, 
        studio, selectedDate, selectedTime, selectedServices, form, errorMsg, timeSlots, services, 
        loginAdmin, secretClick, fetchAdminSchedule, adminSelectDate, toggleOpenDate, fetchBookings, 
        selectStudio, isDateOpen, selectDate, selectTime, toggleService, submitBooking, canProceed, 
        quizCompleted, quizStep, quizQuestions, recommendedService, answerQuiz, resetQuiz, 
        nextStep, prevStep, goToConfirmation, calculateEndTime
    };
  }
}).mount('#app');
</script>
